text: Marcel Stenzel (born 17 February 1992) is a German football player. He plays currently for FC Brünninghausen. ==Career== He made his professional debut for MSV Duisburg in the 3. Liga on 21 March 2015 in a 4–1 away victory against Borussia Dortmund II. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Dortmund Category:German footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:MSV Duisburg players Category:3.
